"inflexible as <trademark class=\"registered\">UNIX</trademark> disks can "
"have only a limited number of partitions. Instead, <filename>vinum</"
"filename> subdivides a single <trademark class=\"registered\">UNIX</"
"trademark> partition, the <emphasis>drive</emphasis>, into contiguous areas "
"called <emphasis>subdisks</emphasis>, which are used as building blocks for "
